      "writtenOn": "2019-02-22T21:38:24Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Does this also get us subsetting: decoding only a sub-rectangle of a (possibly animated) image?\n\nIf it doesn\u0027t, that\u0027s fine. But I\u0027m curious (not in this CL, but in a follow-up CL) whether subsetting would ideally be done in SkWuffsCodec or in Wuffs.",
      "revId": "9dc6192c17dff2c5f0aae49b51fc2c6c4050d255",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "key": {
        "uuid": "41545ea8_20d4eabe",
